{"tid":2461706,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【懶人包】全球國際品牌拒絕新疆棉花 認識BCI","createTime":"2021-03-25T13:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T13:52:12.000Z","uid":187755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb9f0c3691bb9fc115084d818b4932811b3a9c89","tid":2461706,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:49:26.000Z","msg":"今次新疆棉花事件，一定要認識<strong><span class=\"pink\">BCI</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong>BCI係乜機構? </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBCI全名係Better Cotton Initiative，係一個推廣可持續發展棉花的國際NGO。佢地的工作係包括做棉花認證，佢地會訂一系列生產「可持續發展棉花」的準則比農民、生產商、採購商、零售商參考，同埋負責發放BCI許可證，所以的生產一定要符合BCI標準，先會得到認證。<br />\n咁在2020年10月，<span class=\"red\">BCI認為新疆的棉花生產有「強逼勞動」同埋「侵犯人權」的現象</span>，所以就唔再向新疆棉花發放許可證。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">咁佢唔發許可證咁又點呢?</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全球好多巨型品牌都係BCI的會員，例如Guess、Inditex(即係Zara)、H&amp;M、Ikea、Walmart、Adidas、Camper、Burberry、Diesel、Fast Retailing(即係UNIQLO)，<span class=\"red\">咁如果你D貨源係有來自新疆的綿花，好自然你就拎唔到BCI的認證</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBCI會員名單可以係度搵到: <a href=\"https://bettercotton.org/find-members/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbettercotton.org%2Ffind-members%2F&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2Fkv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=ec429044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bettercotton.org/find-members/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">咁拎唔到認證又點?</span></strong><br />\n大家應該仲記得，好多年前，上面唔少的外面品牌都被爆過在亞洲做血汗工廠，唔理工人死活，不斷壓低成本，當年有好多輿論壓力，佢地品牌的形象都好差。呢十年幾年，各大國際企業都放左好多錢去做形象工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其中一樣野，就係參加唔同的認證計劃。例如你見到H&amp;M的價錢牌，會用FSC認證的再造紙去印，仲有organic 或者Fairtrade認證，令到消費者支持自己品牌(支那人除外，佢地連乜野係可持續發展、侵犯人權都唔知)。正因為咁，<span class=\"red\">BCI出左聲唔認新疆棉花，佢下面的會員都跟機。所以大家先見到點解呢兩日一時間咁多品牌出聲同新疆棉花割蓆。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">Eason唔同adidas合作，可以同咩品牌合作?</span></strong><br />\n唔知道Eason知唔知道呢件事的來龍去脈啦，如果Eason唔同任何唔用新疆棉花的公司合作，咁佢真係要上去BCI網站望下個會員名單囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong>我地可以做d咩?</strong></span><br />\n宜家支那人反應咁大，當然一個月之後就會唔記得左啦，但係最重要係D國際企業肯企硬! 最好的畫面係，支那人及奶共偽人長期杯葛，國際品牌繼續唔用新疆棉花，事件要再發酵大D，令到外國人都了解來龍去脈，支持呢D品牌企硬! <span class=\"red\">宜家除左我地留意呢件事之外，歐美相對黎講未係好多人講，大家有時間，就上twitter、Redditt 幫手做下文宣，支持呢d同新疆棉花割蓆的國際品牌，就係我地的任務!</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位幫手補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecd741d6cb3507db93c6c78f9f24b8e65f7c53a","tid":2461706,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS2mZLxjNJwqZnH8fojKAcfLuBXUWCx9ten9LQq5HKuYu?filename=j8UGcdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8UGcdf.jpg&h=205e38bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc7c661fca253ed3d22cc41a44191db92b86dcd3","tid":2461706,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVPZN6wzC98gPPhebMWMB1fWbJ7R2QHkcWeCc8i1B4EDq?filename=6wi7SdE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wi7SdE.jpg&h=4756e86a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}